---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';

const updatedAt = new Date('2025-08-13');
---

<Layout title="Now">
    <article class="h-entry">
        <h1 class="p-name">What I'm up to</h1>
        <time class="date" datetime={updatedAt.toISOString()}>
            Updated {
                updatedAt.toLocaleDateString('en-US', {
                    dateStyle: 'medium',
                })
            }
        </time>

        <content class="e-content">
            <h2>Career</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Tinkering with self-hosted services. Most of them are my daily drivers. I use <a href="https://linkding.link/">LinkDing</a>, <a href="https://github.com/burhan-syed/troddit">Troddit</a>, <a href="https://www.freshrss.org/">FreshRSS</a>, <a href="https://n8n.io">n8n</a> and <a href="https://www.usememos.com/">Memos</a></li>
                <li>Having so much fun automating things with n8n. I now have my own AI chatbot in LINE Messenger app, but still figuring out a way to do the same in <a href="https://signal.org/">Signal</a>.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Artist</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>🎵🥩 24th August - DJing at a beef restaurant.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Education</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Learning Japanese 🇯🇵 through Anki, reading e-books and daily work. I recognized several words and phrase, but not able to form sentences right now.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Music</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z2M1pQY27KA">Jude & Frank - Joga Joga</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kfduUMGOmoY">4EVE - Snooze</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pnY7m5CK-as">Men I Trust - Seven</a></li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Video Games</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Genshin Impact</li>
                <li>Warframe</li>
                <li>Roblox</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Personal</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    📕 Reading <a
                        href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/30646587-the-simple-path-to-wealth"
                        >The Simple Path to Wealth</a
                    >.
                </li>
                <li>Looking forward to enjoy my time at a friend's house. I recently slept over for 2 days and had a great time; food party, DJing, watching Dandadan and Sakamoto Days. I'll be visiting them again next week.</li>
                <li>🏋️‍♂️ Working out 2 days/week and eating healthy.</li>
                <li>Picking up journaling again.</li>
            </ul>
        </content>
    </article>
</Layout>

<style>
    .e-content {
        display: block;
        margin-top: 3rem;
    }

    h2 {
        margin-block: 1.5rem 0.75rem;
    }

    ul,
    p {
        margin-block: 0;
    }
</style>
